Name: Pharmacologic Drug Class
Description: Class of medications based on pharmacologic properties as opposed to therapeutic properties

Name: Indicator
Description: An indicator calculated from certain measures

Name: Radiology/Imaging Procedure
Description: A radiology or imaging test or procedure

Name: InteractSet
Description: Set of drugs that interact with parent drug

Name: Medical supply
Description: Durable medical equipment and other supplies

Name: Test
Description: Acq. during patient encounter (vitals, labs, etc.)

Name: Symptom/Finding
Description: Observation that can be reported from patient or found on exam

Name: Misc Order
Description: Orderable items which aren't tests or drugs

Name: Misc
Description: Terms which don't fit other categories
